      "translation_date": "2025-12-22T08:13:21.5523369Z",
      "original_text": "\"Go away, mon-keigh.\" {n}You hear no hint of irony in the Aeldari's voice.{/n}",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2025-12-22T08:13:21.5523377Z",
          "locale_text": "「消えろ、モンキー」{n}アエルダリの声には皮肉が全く感じられない。{/n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«Márchate, mon-keigh». {n}La voz del {g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}Aeldari{/g}no admite réplica.{/n}",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-05T09:57:16.0484064Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-05T09:57:16.0484065Z",
      "original_text": "\"Leave, mon-keigh.\" {n}The {g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}Aeldari{/g}'s voice is matter-of-fact.{/n}",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-05T09:57:16.0484077Z",
          "locale_text": "«Márchate, mon-keigh». {n}La voz del {g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}Aeldari{/g}no admite réplica.{/n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“走开，猴子。”{n}{g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}艾达灵族{/g}语气平淡地说道。{/n}",
      "modification_date": "2026-05-05T10:00:00.5505981Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-05T10:00:00.5505982Z",
      "original_text": "\"Leave, mon-keigh.\" {n}The {g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}Aeldari{/g}'s voice is matter-of-fact.{/n}",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-05T10:00:00.5505987Z",
          "locale_text": "“走开，猴子。”{n}{g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}艾达灵族{/g}语气平淡地说道。{/n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "deDE",
      "text": "\"Geht, Chem-Pan-Sey.\" {n}Die Stimme des {g|Encyclopedia:AeldariGlossary}Aeldari{/g} ist nüchtern.{/n}",
